---
<section class="relative bg-brand-bg py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-12 px-5 sm:px-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] lg:gap-16 lg:px-8">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3 font-body text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-muted">
        <span class="inline-block h-px w-10 bg-brand-accent"></span>
        The story
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-[clamp(1.9rem,4.5vw,3rem)] font-black uppercase leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.01em] text-brand-text">
        Meet Brian, the electrician <span class="text-brand-secondary">behind Powerhub Electrical</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-muted">
        I was born in rural Vietnam and came to Australia with my mum after losing my dad in an accident when I was young. Growing up, I learned that looking after the people around you is what gets returned to you later, and that shaped how I run this business.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-muted">
        I started my apprenticeship at twenty and have spent the past ten years on the tools, moving from commercial construction into residential maintenance because I preferred the direct contact with homeowners.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-muted">
        Powerhub Electrical began in 2023, and I still personally scope many of the jobs across St Ives and the wider Ku-ring-gai area, including the established, character homes you'll find near <a href="https://www.krg.nsw.gov.au/Planning-and-development/Projects-and-current-works/St-Ives" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-semibold text-brand-secondary underline decoration-brand-accent/50 underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-accent">Ku-ring-gai Council's own planning updates for St Ives</a>. Outside work, you'll usually find me at the gym, at a local cafe, or at the beach with my partner and our corgi.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal relative" style="transition-delay: 120ms;">
      <div class="relative bg-brand-secondary/25 p-0.5 shadow-2xl shadow-black/60" style="clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 90%, 90% 100%, 0 100%);">
        <div class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden" style="clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 90%, 90% 100%, 0 100%);">
          <img src="/images/powerhub/home/work-6.webp" alt="Brian Ho, director of Powerhub Electrical, on site in St Ives" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-3 h-24 w-1.5 bg-brand-accent"></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
